messages.content: Which versions of the Failfast ComfyUI Extensions are currently receiving security updates?
The 0.x.x version series of the Failfast ComfyUI Extensions is currently supported with security updates.
How can I report a vulnerability in the Failfast ComfyUI Extensions?
To report a vulnerability, contact the project maintainers through the provided channels. Expect updates on your report and understand the process for accepted or declined vulnerabilities.
